						<p><hi rend="bold">c. 10th Century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>Mutilated. Register an endowment for offerings and for burning a perpetual lamp. Mentions the sluice <hi rend="italic">(kumiḻi)</hi> committee of Kāvēripākkam, and a decision to collect <hi rend="italic">uṇaṅgal</hi> (voluntary offerings) for feeding and lamp service in the temple of Mahādēva.</p>						

